=head1 DESCRIPTION

The action to deliver incoming emails to an Amazon Q Business
application for indexing.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 ActionFailurePolicy => Str

A policy that states what to do in the case of failure. The action will
fail if there are configuration errors. For example, the specified
application has been deleted or the role lacks necessary permissions to
call the C<qbusiness:BatchPutDocument> API.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> ApplicationId => Str

The unique identifier of the Amazon Q Business application instance
where the email content will be delivered.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> IndexId => Str

The identifier of the knowledge base index within the Amazon Q Business
application where the email content will be stored and indexed.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> RoleArn => Str

The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the IAM Role to use while delivering
to Amazon Q Business. This role must have access to the
C<qbusiness:BatchPutDocument> API for the given application and index.



